{"tid":633391,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老：冇我嘅世盃就唔係世盃","createTime":"2018-04-18T09:24:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T13:47:23.000Z","uid":94771,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e9639ebc2326608c5e381c6baa91d9dc03a542c7","tid":633391,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T09:24:52.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=tqRGKOaiWHhoCo5CzJ7%2Bzozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=7612d7e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】別以為這是伊巴謙莫域的一個肯定答案，他繼續為會否復出踢國家隊賣關子，但可肯定，他一定會在世界盃決賽周期間亮相，只是不知以甚麼身份出席而已。<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域（Zlatan Ibrahimovic）近日言論離不開世界盃，他日前在一個電視直播節目中透露：「我會出發參與世界盃，是的，如果我多言，他們會把我問吊，所以我要小心發言。」<br />\n<br />\n「一個沒有我的世界盃，就不是世界盃。」未知上述言論是否一種暗示，但兩個月的世界盃必可看到其身影，即使他不代表瑞典出賽，在俄羅斯仍不愁沒事可做，因為這位36歲洛杉磯銀河前鋒日前已跟Visa信用卡簽約，成為他們在今夏世界盃決賽周推廣活動的招牌。<br />\n<br />\nVisa較早前在聲明中指，伊巴曾經在7個不同國家征戰同時能夠說5種語言，因此充分表現出品牌的國際性。伊巴霸氣地表示：「Visa當然會找我合作，因為我是Zlatan，是場上最佳的球員，而Visa則是付款界別的最佳。」<br />\n<br />\n曾經為瑞典國家隊上陣擁有116場攻入62球，伊巴早前已宣佈退役，但最近的言論予人感覺他有機會重返國家隊，為國於世界盃決賽周爭取佳績，上周，他已在twitter拋出一句：「我出戰世界盃的機會高唱入雲。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/2/942/21109724942/21118478445_599x420.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F2%2F942%2F21109724942%2F21118478445_599x420.jpg&h=766e8f0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">死廢老</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea15aab0cbda8176bac03192755ccf50ebb15794","tid":633391,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T09:26:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">端典RIP</span>"},{"pid":"45192549fdf710f66d8690cf9d676bcd169a04fa","tid":633391,"uid":17853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T09:28:42.000Z","msg":"比班人踢士氣波仲好啦"},{"pid":"5b6b98930d74c4add561cbc3f083434cfdedfd90","tid":633391,"uid":136666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T09:33:42.000Z","msg":"如果選佢就要踢走一個有為外圍賽付出嘅球員,好難服眾喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c04ba0fe4f63be37b036e55d7edc2985bec8e0","tid":633391,"uid":140363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b6b98930d74c4add561cbc3f083434cfdedfd90","tid":633391,"uid":136666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T09:33:42.000Z","msg":"如果選佢就要踢走一個有為外圍賽付出嘅球員,好難服眾喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T13:18:01.000Z","msg":"話唔定有球員傷病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d1e5662f07780e37d44685c53e4e9db3ff915e","tid":633391,"uid":58610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T13:24:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b1861da61e9b7797ddcda79ee1681b975bad6f5a","tid":633391,"uid":58610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T13:25:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac1536d00adc04335f038adaa157ba3d6a154f77","tid":633391,"uid":139573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T13:25:21.000Z","msg":"上年世界杯冇佢係咪唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問霸氣呂布踢過幾多次世界杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d81fa0e8e31f7001e300e35acb6b71f944a609","tid":633391,"uid":58610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T13:27:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66cf05332df4a2c990a9c30d476e7137e78fe513","tid":633391,"uid":139573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42d81fa0e8e31f7001e300e35acb6b71f944a609","tid":633391,"uid":58610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac1536d00adc04335f038adaa157ba3d6a154f77","tid":633391,"uid":139573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T13:25:21.000Z","ms